---
// src/pages/portfolio.astro
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Projects | Portfolio</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 800px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; line-height: 1.6; }
      nav { margin-bottom: 40px; }
      nav a { margin-right: 20px; text-decoration: none; color: #007acc; font-weight: bold; }
      .project { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; background: #fff; }
      .tag { background: #e0f2fe; color: #0369a1; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 5px; display: inline-block; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a>
    </nav>

    <h1>🛠️ Technical Portfolio</h1>
    <p>A collection of cloud-native systems and automation infrastructure I've designed and built.</p>

    <div class="project">
      <h2>1. Multi-Tenant Production K8s Cluster</h2>
      <p>Architected a highly available Kubernetes cluster featuring automated scaling, strict network isolation policies, and secure ingress traffic routing.</p>
      <div>
        <span class="tag">Kubernetes</span>
        <span class="tag">NetworkPolicies</span>
        <span class="tag">Helm</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project">
      <h2>2. GitOps Continuous Delivery Pipeline</h2>
      <p>Established a zero-touch declarative pipeline utilizing ArgoCD to map Git repository states directly to live cluster deployments, eliminating manual infrastructure management.</p>
      <div>
        <span class="tag">GitOps</span>
        <span class="tag">ArgoCD</span>
        <span class="tag">GitHub Actions</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>